    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "この人は、うちが招待したお客様です\nほら、ここにチケットだってちゃんとあります",
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6000,
          "startTime": 6.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.1716100056
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "うちがいつもお世話になってる人なんですけど\n高校の学園祭を、たいそう懐かしがってまして",
      "startTime": 11.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "今日はちょっとでも、参加した気分を味わってほしくて\nうちが用意した制服を着てもらってたんです",
      "startTime": 20.2918216698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.9512918473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "でも事前に、先生方にご相談しとくべきでした\nまさかこんな騒ぎになるなんて、思わんくて……",
      "startTime": 28.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……安易に誘いに乗ってしまった、俺のせいです\n先生方、本当にすみませんでした",
      "startTime": 38.1244339645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.5163027446
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "うちも、学園祭だからと浮かれ過ぎて……\nお騒がせして、本当にすみませんでした",
      "startTime": 45.29154142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.1904753049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（二人で先生に平謝りした結果）\n（「いつも生徒会長として頑張ってるし」ということで）",
      "startTime": 52.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8913.559723000006,
          "startTime": 61.2468930563
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.2971417428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（今回の件は不問にしていただいて）\n（……俺は、どうにか新聞沙汰を免れることが出来た）",
      "startTime": 60.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.2228120488
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.2228120488
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……それで、優\nなんでチケットを忘れたなんて、嘘をついたんだ",
      "startTime": 69,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "だって{user}さん、うちが誘っても\n即座にきっぱりはっきり、断るんやもん",
      "startTime": 75.9726751012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.5260323527
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "せやからうちも、ちょーっと腹立ってもうて",
      "startTime": 79.5260323527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんと、今日しか出来ない\nデートしようって、プランを練り上げたんよ",
      "startTime": 86.0726751012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.6897056423
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "『{user}さんと同級生だったら』を\n体験出来るのは、今日しかないと思って",
      "startTime": 92.3726751012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あれは、優が『デート』とか言ってからかうから……\nただまぁ、すぐに断ったのは悪かったよ",
      "startTime": 100.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.1379144831
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "でも次からは、もうちょっと穏便な仕返しにしてくれ\nさっきは本当に、肝が冷えたんだから",
      "startTime": 108.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ。でも、何事もなく済んだやないですか",
      "startTime": 111.5386624816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.5461684389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、先生達のお墨付きももらいましたし\n本番まで、もうちょい展示を見て回りましょか",
      "startTime": 120.3822210632,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3399.9999999999914,
          "startTime": 123.7822210632
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.7822210632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ、佐藤さん？\nどないしたん、そんなに慌てて",
      "startTime": 126.6822271667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.7010494076
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　今すぐ生徒会室に来てくれって",
      "startTime": 129.8467595319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.0788876378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか、緊急事態みたいだな\n俺は一人で大丈夫だから、優はそっちに行ってきてくれ",
      "startTime": 136.6333485921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.3741256241
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "うう……もう少し、{user}さんと\n制服デートしたかったんやけどなぁ",
      "startTime": 143.6792036059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.2635358973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "すみませんけど、生徒会室行ってきます\nミュージカルは絶対上演するから、楽しみにしといてな",
      "startTime": 151.1125369392,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4506.713310999999,
          "startTime": 155.6192502502
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.470386208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……生徒会長も大変だな\nあ、そろそろ、制服から着替えてもいいよな……？",
      "startTime": 158.470386208,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5667.344406699982,
          "startTime": 164.1377306147
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.8877306147
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.8877306147
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.1377306147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（そして、生徒会室では紆余曲折あったようだが）\n（無事に、ミュージカルの上演が始まった）",
      "startTime": 169.2333485921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（まさか、琴乃達まで出演するとはなぁ……）\n（放送で呼び出してた時は、何事かと思ったけど）",
      "startTime": 177.9666819255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "その人達に罪はない……！\n取り憑くなら、私に取り憑きなさい……！",
      "startTime": 184.9774393402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "っ、理性が溶けてしまいそう……でも、受け止めて\nみせる。たとえ悪魔でも、分かりあいたい、から……",
      "startTime": 194.3823611702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（しかしみんな、ぶっつけ本番なのにさすがだな）\n（お客さん達も、盛り上がってるし）",
      "startTime": 204.800024414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
